Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.26,1:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Emma, we ought to start looking at that, don't you suppose?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.26,1:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Having Mind Mastery
