Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.26,1:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.69,1:09:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a possibility for us to make it in this lifetime or is this still a many lifetime experience?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.14,1:09:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the requirement is extraordinary and so therefore fewer number because the demand is extraordinary,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.07,1:09:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not that people couldn't, but the willingness to say yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.07,1:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you can get off the bus at certain levels, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.07,1:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and most get off the bus on a letter and not going to see it all the way through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.55,1:10:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a matter of commitment and...
