Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.55,1:10:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...and discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.55,1:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, tenacity of the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.44,1:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And also you have to have some awareness of what the levels are so you get some idea of where you are
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.44,1:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether you want to continue on further.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.44,1:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there's no rush, you don't have to get there, you know, in this lifetime, you know, anyway.
