Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.72,1:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there was some prior contract within myself to go further, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.81,1:10:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There was some prior contract, understanding agreement, understanding agreement, yeah.
