Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.30,1:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As one's profession, avocation, commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.02,1:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like when I couldn't see one more patient and they would call.
