Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.64,1:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And it goes right over people's heads.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.64,1:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, for absolutely free, in a matter of seconds, you can find the absolute truth
