Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.73,1:17:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.18,1:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the karmic consequence of that and how can they undo that how can you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.69,1:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,undo that you've killed the you know 50,000 people how can you undo that you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.14,1:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,may not have culpability but you've got responsibility because you're ignorant
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.34,1:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't have any culpability in the form of ignorance I mean in the form of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.77,1:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,sin see because you were too ignorant to know that was sinful but you do have
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.89,1:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,responsibility so even though you hit somebody with your car
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.47,1:18:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,say it's not your responsibility you're still accountable in the court understand
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.03,1:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's moral responsibility and culpability and moral responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.53,1:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,manslaughter means yes you did kill that person culpability means to what degree
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.10,1:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are you guilty
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.46,1:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you might have maximum responsibility and zero guilt or might be other way
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.64,1:18:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,around because your intention was to kill them just cause you didn't manage
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.02,1:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.52,1:18:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,mean that you didn't try. So there's group responsibilities. So my understanding, because
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.44,1:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we did the distribution of the consciousness levels on the planet, you see great hordes
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.86,1:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of people tend to come in at certain consciousness calibrations, and they all tend to distribute
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.98,1:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves in the same places on the planet, the same continents. Other continents are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.21,1:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of a completely different calibration level, and they seem to come in together. They have
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.65,1:19:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,different lessons to learn, you see. There's individual as well as group karma, culpability
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.36,1:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and accountability, you see. Also, even though you didn't agree, once you cheer something
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.72,1:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,on, you join the karmic responsibility. You don't have to be out there killing people
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.53,1:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the killing field, but the fact that you cheer Hitler on and march with a goose step
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.50,1:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and his...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.64,1:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,army, you are giving him support, and now you are taking on part of the karmic responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.47,1:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Nazi fascism. You didn't have to be out there actually killing the person in
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.76,1:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a uniform, but the fact that you cheered on the Fuhrer to kill, in the end, it amounted
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.31,1:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to 10 million or 100 million, God knows what. You take on some responsibility. So the apologists
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.85,1:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for evil, you see, even though they do not personally commit it, you see, they are doing
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.85,1:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.85,1:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They are taking on a certain responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.85,1:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're just going to the market to shop, the person that gets killed, why did
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.85,1:20:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that person get killed and not...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.85,1:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.19,1:20:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The person next to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.19,1:20:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you're in the market and you were shopping and the car came through and hit the person
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.19,1:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,next to you, but not you. What would be the purpose of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.75,1:20:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're looking for a logical purpose. Karma doesn't work that way. It works as propensities,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.86,1:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,collective propensities in very ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.75,1:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.75,1:20:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're often in group form, you see. You have to think of the difference between accountability
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.89,1:20:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and culpability. Once you understand that, it resolves it. As I said before, being born
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.36,1:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a human, you already have a karmic past, do you not? What do you need a savior for?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.76,1:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.10,1:21:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically, you're born with a need for a savior already, your original sin, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.35,1:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think it's an issue too complex for me to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.11,1:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think only divinity, you see. Why is it whole races, generation after generation,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.07,1:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are wiped out over and over again, see? So why do we choose to reincarnate within that
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.15,1:21:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,particular race, knowing its karmic propensities? We choose to be that which we become.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.43,1:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we only have a half hour left and I know there's a lot of questions. We have
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.19,1:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to be out of here...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.19,1:21:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, run faster, faster, faster, faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.19,1:21:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...at 5 o'clock. So if there's anyone in line here...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.19,1:21:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone in line here that have books that we need to sign or they want signed,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.19,1:21:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do them now in case we run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.19,1:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So the books can come from this way and the questions can come from this way. Is that
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.19,1:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we're doing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.19,1:22:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.19,1:22:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.19,1:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.22,1:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.22,1:22:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.82,1:22:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.82,1:22:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was going to do this. I want to say thank you for your work, your wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.81,1:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,books.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.27,1:22:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.27,1:22:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard during reading Devotional Nonduality that coming here was allowing me to speak
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.27,1:22:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to the allness through David Hawkins. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.27,1:22:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.27,1:22:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming here allows you to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.59,1:22:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.59,1:22:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, through you. Is she speaking to the allness?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.59,1:22:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It occurred to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.43,1:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any other reality except the allness. Yes, you're always speaking to the allness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.43,1:22:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.43,1:22:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know the reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.43,1:22:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But your experience going through the door was...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.90,1:22:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.90,1:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.90,1:22:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.90,1:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.90,1:22:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.90,1:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.96,1:22:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.23,1:22:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.23,1:22:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.23,1:23:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a thrive.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.23,1:23:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.23,1:23:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.65,1:23:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.65,1:23:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,... your experience going through the doorway to the ultimate death of ego...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.65,1:23:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.65,1:23:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,... and experiencing the transcendence, the allness, you gave up yourself, your small
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.85,1:23:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,S-E-L-F.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.85,1:23:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.85,1:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are existing here with a straight shot. It's like...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.25,1:23:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're all divine and we're...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.25,1:23:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.85,1:23:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To say, you know, we have divine guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.76,1:23:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.76,1:23:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.06,1:23:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The sacrifice of the small self really allows the large self
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.43,1:23:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to become dominant, up-revealing, and any sense of separation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.97,1:23:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try and cite it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.34,1:23:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get transmission of your energy through your DVDs as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.56,1:23:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just watching your review of the work for 2006.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.47,1:24:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the energy of the speaker?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.40,1:24:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can write on there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.13,1:24:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the speaker transmits through the, what did she call that thing, a DVD?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.35,1:24:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,DVD.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.89,1:24:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A DVD.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.47,1:24:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.35,1:24:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.73,1:24:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,DVDs and DVDs and CDs and a whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.89,1:24:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassettes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.22,1:24:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.71,1:24:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And now there's a toy player that you can make a play on.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.06,1:24:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,iPod.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.51,1:24:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,iPod.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.13,1:24:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I do a portrait of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.68,1:24:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I do a portrait of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.23,1:24:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,May she do a portrait?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.80,1:24:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an artist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.88,1:24:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Went to the Art Institute in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.00,1:24:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.93,1:24:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.39,1:24:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.23,1:24:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do it in a second, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.53,1:24:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.68,1:24:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.06,1:24:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.02,1:24:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.65,1:24:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.02,1:24:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this has been a little...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.05,1:24:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan, do you have a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.97,1:24:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.14,1:25:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother-in-law has served two tours in Iraq, and he has orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.23,1:25:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother-in-law, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.85,1:25:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Has served two tours in Iraq, and he has orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.64,1:25:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His orders for February.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.97,1:25:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.47,1:25:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's been talking to me in the evening about the atrocities and the killing that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.61,1:25:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he commits, and I tell him about exactly what you said today about the fly, in terms of
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.07,1:25:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't actually kill something, but when I'm talking to him, I would love to have a
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.57,1:25:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,bug in my ear to say what you would say to someone, because I'm not really qualified.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.02,1:25:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to relieve his anguish?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.18,1:25:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.18,1:25:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or just understand or have compassion?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.42,1:25:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say to somebody who...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.56,1:25:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say to somebody who was going through that anguish?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.56,1:25:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to relieve his anguish about what he has to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.56,1:25:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.56,1:25:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.56,1:25:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also don't want him to feel so guilty that he gets himself killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.56,1:25:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me six questions now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.56,1:25:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.56,1:25:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.56,1:25:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to relieve his anguish.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.56,1:25:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I would like to know what I should say, or what you would say.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.56,1:26:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say to someone that had to serve a tour in Iraq and...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.56,1:26:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.56,1:26:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is their intention?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.56,1:26:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to relieve his anguish?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.56,1:26:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His guilt?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.56,1:26:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.56,1:26:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to say to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.56,1:26:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he doing good about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.56,1:26:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to find his peace with what he's...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.56,1:26:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.56,1:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like him to find his peace with what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.56,1:26:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's worried about him not having peace with the actions that he has to commit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.56,1:26:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.56,1:26:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it could take a lifetime to recontextualize that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.56,1:26:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing his duty as he sees that he must do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.56,1:26:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one priority.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.03,1:26:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.03,1:26:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So then he has to understand the difference between responsibility and culpability, et
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.03,1:26:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.03,1:26:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take him some years of spiritual work to come to terms with it, and that's one of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.26,1:26:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the reasons for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.26,1:26:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of human life, the value of under what conditions.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.88,1:26:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is sacrificing your life for a higher principle?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.03,1:27:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's his spiritual work to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.27,1:27:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only be of help to give him alternate ways he could go with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.28,1:27:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a profound and difficult thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.28,1:27:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.28,1:27:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.96,1:27:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's been in the service to evaluate ethically, morally, spiritually, ethically,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.23,1:27:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,morally, spiritually, psychologically, the value and consequences of all the decisions
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.85,1:27:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you've made.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.85,1:27:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just about killing people.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.85,1:27:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's many other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.85,1:27:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The camaraderie, the loyalty, the love of your brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.52,1:27:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The love of the brothers lasts a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.48,1:27:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe to love others as much or greater than yourself could be the greatest lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.75,1:27:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on what the lesson is karmically in his lifetime for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.75,1:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned to love beyond all restriction, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.15,1:28:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us together, forever loved and do love, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.43,1:28:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.35,1:28:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We forgive and love each other forever, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.21,1:28:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what I learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.15,1:28:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, he may have something different to learn.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.15,1:28:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.15,1:28:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.15,1:28:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We are sending DVDs to several servicemen over there at this time, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.15,1:28:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They have called and ordered them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.15,1:28:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.15,1:28:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we are sending them, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.15,1:28:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So he might be learning unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.15,1:28:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's what I learned, to let nothing stand.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.15,1:28:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what my brother did.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.15,1:29:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to have us all crying here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.44,1:29:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.44,1:29:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.93,1:29:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A mutual friend of ours, Marcy and Wayne Dyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.93,1:29:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with Marcy last summer, and Wayne was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.93,1:29:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was telling me about this healer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.93,1:29:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He was real.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.27,1:29:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Healer?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.27,1:29:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.27,1:29:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The John of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.27,1:29:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.80,1:29:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to calibrate John of God?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.80,1:29:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.80,1:29:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.48,1:29:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.48,1:29:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.48,1:29:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.48,1:29:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We just don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.48,1:29:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to ask permission?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.48,1:29:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.48,1:29:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.48,1:29:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.48,1:29:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.84,1:29:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After I talk with you, it will help me decide.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.84,1:29:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.93,1:29:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was going to get your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.93,1:29:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.93,1:29:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.71,1:29:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.71,1:29:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.71,1:29:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.71,1:29:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.71,1:29:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.71,1:29:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.71,1:29:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.71,1:29:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.27,1:29:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask we have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.98,1:29:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.98,1:29:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have permission, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.43,1:29:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.43,1:29:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's up to you, karmically, to make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.43,1:29:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the will to get well will be operative no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.50,1:29:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So your belief and your capacity to get well, anybody could be the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.50,1:30:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.50,1:30:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.50,1:30:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it could be none.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.64,1:30:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.64,1:30:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I get a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.64,1:30:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to give away your power to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.64,1:30:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.64,1:30:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.78,1:30:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.78,1:30:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.78,1:30:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.78,1:30:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.78,1:30:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.48,1:30:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.48,1:30:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.97,1:30:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.00,1:30:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.00,1:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.00,1:30:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.00,1:30:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.00,1:30:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.00,1:30:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.00,1:30:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.43,1:30:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.43,1:30:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.76,1:30:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.76,1:30:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.76,1:30:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of an ailment.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.76,1:30:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.76,1:30:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll cure itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.76,1:30:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.76,1:30:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can guarantee you a .
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.76,1:30:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.76,1:30:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.76,1:30:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.76,1:30:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.76,1:30:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep it to myself, I never hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.76,1:30:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.27,1:31:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.27,1:31:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.27,1:31:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My question concerns consciousness level 600 and non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.27,1:31:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,According to your books, once a person reaches this level, there's no identification with
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.27,1:31:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.27,1:31:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No separation between the self and the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.61,1:31:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say all sense of a personal self disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.89,1:31:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, isn't there still some awareness, witness, localized in a body?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.03,1:31:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if the soul leaves the body, isn't there still a personal soul?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.38,1:31:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So each of us has our own unique experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.65,1:31:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't that be considered...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.61,1:31:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you worrying about? I don't get what you're worrying about.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.27,1:31:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.35,1:31:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you worrying about level 600?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.02,1:31:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to understand what it means to get to that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.23,1:31:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you stop thinking about yourself as a self-existent causal agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.72,1:32:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal self making decisions or doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.10,1:32:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking there's a separate causal entity called me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.98,1:32:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.32,1:32:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it continues on doing that because of the constant gains.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.90,1:32:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As you keep surrendering the gains, there's no gain to believing that anymore and it stops doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.44,1:32:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly you go into a high state of joy and bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.64,1:32:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfection of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.27,1:32:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from 500 lovingness to 540 unconditional lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.44,1:32:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the love intensifies.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.39,1:32:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By 570 it becomes saintly.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.47,1:32:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By 580, 590 it becomes ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.97,1:33:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Extreme ecstasy, you can dance for days non-stop without eating, drinking, sleeping, tirelessly, day after day, endless, ecstatic joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.60,1:33:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.30,1:33:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This too, O Lord, must be laid down to thee, O Lord, and you lay down the ecstasy, you lay down the ecstasy to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.67,1:33:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the ultimate of all highs, beyond methadrine, beyond anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.89,1:33:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you can expect.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.61,1:33:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This too, O Lord, must be laid down.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.27,1:33:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you lay down your ecstasy and surrender that to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.03,1:33:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then comes on a piece of such profundity as beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.43,1:33:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond which there is nothing more desired or wanted, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.23,1:33:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if consciousness and life goes on, it does because of some karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.88,1:33:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's no personal you to make a decision about such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.03,1:33:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.84,1:33:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.77,1:33:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This too, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.68,1:34:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.92,1:34:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.35,1:34:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.27,1:34:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.18,1:34:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am moving as fast as I can move, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.60,1:34:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.23,1:34:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.17,1:34:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.98,1:34:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask a question that has to do with oneness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.32,1:34:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've spoken, I hear you mention a lot of times, the self of the teacher with the capital S, or the self of the student.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.52,1:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering, is there not just one self?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.82,1:34:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there more than one?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.78,1:34:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.39,1:34:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same self.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.81,1:34:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.47,1:34:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which is looking out through me is identical to that which is looking out through all others?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.60,1:34:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.25,1:34:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that it is one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.01,1:35:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the capacity for conscious awareness of existence to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.48,1:35:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which everybody has already inherited by virtue of being human, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.78,1:35:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you realize that this is an impersonal quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.32,1:35:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quality of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.59,1:35:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you stop thinking of it as a product.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.43,1:35:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop thinking of it as a product.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.44,1:35:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop thinking of it as a product.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.48,1:35:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop thinking of it as a product.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.55,1:35:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop thinking of it as a personal I that has, you know, reached that state of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.44,1:35:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same I.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.25,1:35:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.36,1:35:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.42,1:35:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.27,1:35:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.73,1:35:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.11,1:35:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.92,1:35:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In case I blink.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.89,1:35:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.35,1:35:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.77,1:35:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.43,1:35:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You answered my questions already.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.65,1:35:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.31,1:35:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just wanted to tell you that I wanted to thank you for liberating me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.77,1:35:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.06,1:36:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying religion since I was 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.56,1:36:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I entered a seminary at 12 and I was so frustrated and confused and you liberated everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.96,1:36:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.56,1:36:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.15,1:36:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.85,1:36:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.64,1:36:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.73,1:36:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, could you expand on contemplation and surrender and how I can improve that skills?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.65,1:36:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.59,1:36:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation is more subtle than meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.71,1:36:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.67,1:36:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.47,1:36:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of holding something in mind as an attraction to divinity to reveal the answer to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.05,1:36:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a mudra.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.94,1:36:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold what is the highest service to go to California and speak to a large group?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.19,1:37:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the highest service to the old Lord?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.10,1:37:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To say and sustain that which depends on my love for survival or to really represent an energy
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.25,1:37:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.13,1:37:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.13,1:37:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a yin kind of an approach, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.88,1:37:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation is more like a yin in which I draw from the infinite wisdom, unknowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.31,1:37:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the question, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.23,1:37:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplative lifestyle is a very yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.68,1:37:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does surrender fit into that along with contemplation?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.86,1:37:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean by yin?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.32,1:37:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.00,1:37:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.00,1:37:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.03,1:37:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.06,1:37:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.14,1:37:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.27,1:37:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.38,1:37:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.50,1:37:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.56,1:37:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.65,1:37:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.69,1:37:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By being.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.22,1:37:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The supplication.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.69,1:37:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity cannot refuse you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.57,1:38:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have permission?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.64,1:38:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity cannot refuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.81,1:38:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.18,1:38:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.71,1:38:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.14,1:38:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have God at your service.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.51,1:38:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.48,1:38:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.75,1:38:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.35,1:38:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God is at your service.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.50,1:38:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, a spiritual teacher sees himself as being at your service.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.53,1:38:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is to be at the service of the student.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.27,1:38:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.81,1:38:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.60,1:38:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.57,1:38:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated earlier, come here, by devotion, Krishna says, thou art mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.68,1:39:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Since all questions come and go, and tomorrow or a year from now we will all forget about what we asked or what we talked about,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.07,1:39:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to spend a few moments in your presence, in your stillness, if it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.88,1:39:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now doing so. It is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.81,1:39:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.14,1:39:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.48,1:39:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.52,1:39:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a very quick question. Is the spiritual energy the same thing as the Holy Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.30,1:40:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. Well, yes, it is. I see how you're asking it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.31,1:40:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.31,1:40:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an energy field of consciousness which you can now calibrate extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.22,1:40:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier today I understood you to say that if a person calibrates below 200, that you really can't talk with that person.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.22,1:40:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.22,1:40:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're talking on a different plane, yes. You can talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.57,1:40:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, if a nation calibrates below 200 and they do acts of violence, how do we as a nation respond from power rather than force?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.57,1:40:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you. I couldn't tell you. See, what you value is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.43,1:41:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say I think democracy is the most wonderful thing in the world. You should have it. I'm going to sit in your seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.28,1:41:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is such a stupid cuckoo man. I don't know how I give him any time and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.28,1:41:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To give the common man a vote is the dumbest thing I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.07,1:41:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so ignorant and stupid. If he wasn't, he wouldn't be worshipping me as his savior.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.46,1:41:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalin, Hitler, all the great ones, Ivan the Terrible, all thought the populists were scum.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.44,1:41:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they'll tell you they're scum.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.44,1:41:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler thought all the Germans deserved to die for losing the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.01,1:41:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And, generation after generation, you know how you can tell it's coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.35,1:41:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, it always goose steps. It always does the goose step.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.63,1:41:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It always has a big picture that they carry of the leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.63,1:42:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They all pledge allegiance to the leader. They all cheer.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.17,1:42:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And they all die in the end. Always the same signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.85,1:42:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over, man doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.85,1:42:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The goose step. The goose step. Don't you see the goose step, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.89,1:42:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The militarism. Dying for the leader in the great posters over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.10,1:42:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you tell people like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.10,1:42:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you read history books? What should you say to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.35,1:42:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we as individuals...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.35,1:42:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.35,1:42:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray for them. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.35,1:42:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It caused me to cry over and over and over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.78,1:42:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The same picture, the same story, the same parade, the same goose step.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.10,1:42:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goose step. Generation after generation.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.10,1:42:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at it in today's newsreel, and it's the same as the 1930s when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.10,1:43:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goose step.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.52,1:43:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.52,1:43:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.68,1:43:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I would like to express an infinite gratitude to that which has allowed every truth and wisdom
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.01,1:43:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,come and unfolding through you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.22,1:43:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your work and your staff.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.22,1:43:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just expressing infinite gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.61,1:43:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.61,1:43:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have three sets of pairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.61,1:43:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This keeps coming to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.68,1:43:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have, like, any idea what to make out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.68,1:43:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,First set, and I would like to see if you have an input or if there is a correlation or relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.68,1:43:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right brain, left brain, conscious mind, subconscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.68,1:43:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a relation, correlation?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.23,1:43:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an input?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.90,1:43:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.13,1:43:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.13,1:43:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have three sets of pairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.13,1:43:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.13,1:44:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Three sets of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.13,1:44:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.13,1:44:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.13,1:44:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, right brain and left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.13,1:44:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Conscious mind and subconscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.13,1:44:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any relation, correlation?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.13,1:44:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.14,1:44:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the second.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.14,1:44:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.14,1:44:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right brain and intuition.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.64,1:44:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they one and the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.64,1:44:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right brain and...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.64,1:44:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And intuition.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.64,1:44:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.64,1:44:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not identities.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.64,1:44:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,People process.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.64,1:44:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Instinctual information below consciousness level 200 through their left brain, which
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.81,1:44:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,triggers adrenaline emergency response, fight or flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.81,1:44:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.81,1:44:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,More evolved, over 200, the person now processes things differently with the right brain, in
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.81,1:44:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which they perceive essence, not just appearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.81,1:44:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The left brain is only interested in appearance, and the right brain is interested in what
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.42,1:44:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the essence and the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.42,1:44:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.42,1:44:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.42,1:44:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's more benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.42,1:45:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The right brain puts out oxytoxin, oxytocin, and neurotransmitters, which support peacefulness
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.43,1:45:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and love and caring about other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.43,1:45:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.43,1:45:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.43,1:45:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.43,1:45:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.43,1:45:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The last pair that I have, which you probably have answered, transcending duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.43,1:45:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.43,1:45:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And energizing the right brain through certain activities.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.43,1:45:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if I'm riding with my left hand, this is energizing the right brain?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.43,1:45:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.43,1:45:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.43,1:45:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're just talking about motor activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.43,1:45:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about motor activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.43,1:45:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.43,1:45:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.43,1:45:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not motor activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.43,1:45:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.43,1:45:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have anything to do with handedness.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.43,1:45:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.43,1:45:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.43,1:45:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.43,1:45:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.43,1:45:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending duality and psychoanalysis, removing the blocks between right brain and left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.43,1:45:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Communication.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.43,1:45:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Allowing more communication.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.43,1:45:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why, like, people have denial.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.50,1:46:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They suffer because they try to push things away, not admitting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.52,1:46:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is transcending duality the same as allowing more communication between right brain, left
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.61,1:46:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,brain?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.61,1:46:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.72,1:46:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.77,1:46:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You answered her.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.77,1:46:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand her.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.77,1:46:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.77,1:46:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that the right brain and the left, she's trying to come into that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.85,1:46:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Which side of the brain is non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.85,1:46:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.85,1:46:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in a right-handed person.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.85,1:46:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The right side of the brain, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.85,1:46:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.92,1:46:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.92,1:46:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Does duality exist?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.34,1:46:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.36,1:46:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.36,1:46:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're writing a paper on neurology and psychology and the physiology, neurologic
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.36,1:46:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,physiology of psychology.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.36,1:46:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.36,1:46:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.36,1:46:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have to close.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.36,1:46:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be out of here by five.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.36,1:46:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.36,1:46:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.36,1:46:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.36,1:46:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got a quick question, you can be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.36,1:46:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to be precise and quick?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.36,1:46:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.36,1:46:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.36,1:46:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.36,1:46:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.36,1:46:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.36,1:46:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.36,1:46:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.36,1:46:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.36,1:46:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.36,1:46:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.36,1:46:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.36,1:46:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.52,1:46:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eins, zwei, drei, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.52,1:46:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.52,1:46:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.52,1:47:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.61,1:47:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between preference and positionality?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.61,1:47:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, positionality is a decision, and a preference is merely a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.61,1:47:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So preference is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.61,1:47:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.61,1:47:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.44,1:47:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.44,1:47:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Preference is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.44,1:47:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.44,1:47:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Preference is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.44,1:47:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.44,1:47:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.44,1:47:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Preference is a position.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.77,1:47:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.77,1:47:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.80,1:47:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.80,1:47:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freedom of choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.80,1:47:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.80,1:47:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.80,1:47:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.80,1:47:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.80,1:47:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.80,1:47:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.80,1:47:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.80,1:47:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.80,1:47:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.80,1:47:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too slow with your questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.80,1:47:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up and ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.80,1:47:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.80,1:47:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be out of here right at 5 o'clock, and we cannot answer just the questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.80,1:47:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to get through everyone, and I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.80,1:47:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still wired up.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.80,1:47:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.80,1:47:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I give myself to you as your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.80,1:48:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I dedicate myself to you in return for which God gives me the presence of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.11,1:48:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my presence from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.56,1:48:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.56,1:48:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.56,1:48:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.23,1:48:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.80,1:48:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You all are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.19,1:48:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.19,1:48:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They are a wonderful crowd, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.44,1:48:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.44,1:48:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a little more time to answer them fully.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.05,1:48:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ... I have such a hard time understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.05,1:48:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to shake hands and take pictures on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.05,1:48:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.05,1:48:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
